
Project title
(Image-editor)

Project Description
It is a very simple and basic image editor principal based on the advanced image editor like canvas and other stuff. In this project, I have created a container within the container we have two rows as the first half or rows containing the basic functionality of Image editor.
And the second half of the container is having the upload button and with hideable div that will preview the selected image after clicking on the upload button.

In the functionality we have

- Blur 
- Contrast
- Hue-rotate
- Sepia
- and having with rotate functionality
- no rotate
- horizontal rotate
- vertical rotate

Stack
And in order to tick the check box just put x inside them for example - [x] like this. Please delete options that are not relevant.

- [x] Html
- [x] CSS
- [x] JavaScript


